dc_title_s: Stokes State Forest, New Jersey 1948 maps
dc_creator_sm: State of New Jersey Department of Conservation and Economic Development
dc_description_s: Maps of Stokes State Forest in Sussex County, N.J. part of multi-page brochure. These sheets are two maps of area. First includes inset guide to Kittle Field. Second map shows Tillman Ravine with inset of the western section of the park. Legends indicate paved roads, unpaved trails, streams and other waterways, camp grounds and park office.
